class.comment: Interface for all supported NBT Tags.

OBJECT_HEADER.comment: The header of the NBT Tag that identifies an object type.

ARRAY_HEADER.comment: The header of the NBT Tag that identifies an array type.

OBJECT_REFERENCE.comment: The header of the NBT Tag that identifies an object reference type.

STRING_SIZE.comment: The size of the string header.

TAG_END.comment: The id of the NBT Tag that identifies the end of a compound.

TAG_BYTE.comment: The id of a NBT Tag that identifies a byte.

TAG_SHORT.comment: The id of a NBT Tag that identifies a short.

TAG_INT.comment: The id of a NBT Tag that identifies an int.

TAG_LONG.comment: The id of a NBT Tag that identifies a long.

TAG_FLOAT.comment: The id of a NBT Tag that identifies a float.

TAG_DOUBLE.comment: The id of a NBT Tag that identifies a double.

TAG_BYTE_ARRAY.comment: The id of a NBT Tag that identifies a byte array.

TAG_STRING.comment: The id of a NBT Tag that identifies a string.

TAG_LIST.comment: The id of a NBT Tag that identifies a list.

TAG_COMPOUND.comment: The id of a NBT Tag that identifies a compound.

TAG_INT_ARRAY.comment: The id of a NBT Tag that identifies an int array.

TAG_LONG_ARRAY.comment: The id of a NBT Tag that identifies a long array.

TAG_ANY_NUMERIC.comment: The id of a NBT Tag that identifies any numeric type.

MAX_DEPTH.comment: The maximum depth of a NBT Tag.

write.comment: Writes the NBT Tag to the data output.

return.comment: The string representation of the NBT Tag.

toString.comment: Returns the string representation of the NBT Tag.

return.comment: The id of the NBT Tag.

getId.comment: Fetches the id of the NBT Tag.

return.comment: The type of the NBT Tag.

getType.comment: Fetches the type of the NBT Tag.

return.comment: A copy of the NBT Tag.

copy.comment: Creates a copy of the NBT Tag.

return.comment: The size of the NBT Tag in bytes.

sizeInBytes.comment: Calculates the size of the NBT Tag in bytes.

return.comment: The string representation of the NBT Tag's value.

getAsString.comment: Returns the string representation of the NBT Tag's value.
